videos.description: Morgan Maly drains a nice shot off the glass and a 3-pointer a little later to help Creighton build an early lead over Connecticut.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Morgan Maly helps Creighton to early lead vs. UConn) 2022/2/2 ESHEET

videos.headline: Morgan Maly helps Creighton to early lead vs. UConn

videos.description: Nika Muhl brings Connecticut within two of Creighton after scoring off a steal.

videos.description: Buckets by Christyn Williams, Caroline Ducharme and Aaliyah Edwards help the Huskies turn a deficit into a lead in the third quarter.

videos.headline: UConn starts 3rd quarter strong to take lead over Creighton

videos.description: Christyn Williams sinks a 3-pointer. On the ensuing possession, Creighton turns the ball over, and Williams gets the ball back for another bucket.
